M3MTA
=====

An experimental mail transfer agent using Mojo::IOLoop and MongoDB.

INSTALLATION
------------

    If you're using M3MTA in daemon mode, you'll need to run
    ./install
    to create /var/log/m3mta and /var/run/m3mta before use.

    In console mode, no log file or PID file are required.

STARTING M3MTA
--------------

    Start IMAP, SMTP and MDA:
        ./bin/m3mta start

    Stop IMAP, SMTP and MDA:
        ./bin/m3mta stop

    Start server or MDA in daemon mode:
        ./init.d/m3mta-imap start
        ./init.d/m3mta-smtp start
        ./init.d/m3mta-mda start

    Stop server or MDA in daemon mode:
        ./init.d/m3mta-imap stop
        ./init.d/m3mta-smtp stop
        ./init.d/m3mta-mda stop

    Start server or MDA in console mode:
        ./bin/m3mta-imap start
        ./bin/m3mta-smtp start
        ./bin/m3mta-mda start

        Use Ctrl<C> to stop.

CONFIGURATION
-------------

    Edit ./config.json



